{"tid":815204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"借《蜘蛛俠》電玩場景求婚 點知未出街就分手","createTime":"2018-09-12T00:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T09:10:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5f41fbeb6e980e43b4b80cef3dcb4c63b08e6b72","tid":815204,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T00:53:19.000Z","msg":"蜘蛛俠fans Tyler今年5月喺社交平台twitter出post，<br />\n<br />\n希望開發蜘蛛俠電玩遊戲嘅公司，<br />\n<br />\n可以喺嚟緊推出嘅新game入面，加入幫佢求婚嘅message。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GhgA8TKpguxf5Kp0Nh4HWQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9MzQ0/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/e999cec396dd9e8f2a3306b82c26d514\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FGhgA8TKpguxf5Kp0Nh4HWQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9MzQ0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2Fe999cec396dd9e8f2a3306b82c26d514&h=706fc79f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話晒都係掛住《蜘蛛俠》個名，幫人嘅事又點可以托手跟？<br />\n<br />\n遊戲公司就回Tyler「冇問題，你女友咩名？」。<br />\n<br />\n上星期，遊戲出街。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲嘅彩蛋入面，蜘蛛俠喺戲院前經過，<br />\n<br />\n而戲院門外大牌就寫住 Maddie, will you marry me? 呢句求婚對白。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/idWEuZQTnKlr3Pjdh3dxKg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Nzg4O2g9NDM5/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/057e2d067ab8d01fad53b6130fef90d6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FidWEuZQTnKlr3Pjdh3dxKg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Nzg4O2g9NDM5%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2F057e2d067ab8d01fad53b6130fef90d6&h=3c47cf2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但喺呢一幕面世之前幾個星期&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nTyler同呢位女主角Madison（暱稱Maddie）分。咗。手&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nTyler接受訪問時話，因為（前）女友想有個成村人都睇見嘅求婚，<br />\n<br />\n佢先膽粗粗同遊戲公司聯絡。<br />\n<br />\nTyler又話呢間公司好人到不得了，肯聽佢嘅提議之餘，<br />\n<br />\n搞到而家呢個局面都提出幫佢改咗個畫面。<br />\n<br />\n佢就建議將求婚改為懷念嫲嫲嘅訊息。<br />\n<br />\n未完架！更爆嘅係，殘爆嘅Tyler仲拍條片放上youtube，<br />\n<br />\n表示Maddie嘅新歡係自己嘅兄弟！！<br />\n<br />\n事件經廣泛報導之後，Maddie向傳媒澄清，<br />\n<br />\n佢同Tyler一早就有問題，因為二人關係變到好似阿媽湊仔咁，<br />\n<br />\n成日要提呢樣提嗰樣。<br />\n<br />\nMaddie又強調，係同Tyler分咗手，先同佢嘅兄弟一齊。<br />\n<br />\n精采到咁&hellip;&hellip;不如下一集Spider Man拍返呢個故仔ok？"},{"pid":"195f82cc711260d2943391ff759091d31ed08a89","tid":815204,"uid":2295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T01:00:31.000Z","msg":"起左對姦夫淫婦底未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8f66cb3952dbdaf78fc7fd9b383931961390ef","tid":815204,"uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T01:06:45.000Z","msg":"Btw英文佢直情講brother,唔係我地講老死個隻兄弟"},{"pid":"db7e8e0bdddca0ced5329d24f40422a1e79c86f0","tid":815204,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62b827922e2a29c2c666ebadf5d53577e9220b87","tid":815204,"uid":6799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa08a437701d2f992e0e06af0e0ef2f69ccab0c2","tid":815204,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:32:57.000Z","msg":"懷念嫲嫲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d66e9e21428602a1cef503deb182b1e1ac95a2","tid":815204,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:36:15.000Z","msg":"佢親呀哥 橙"},{"pid":"6b264a91a1f58021fee2fb4099a012846f7243da","tid":815204,"uid":49208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:38:22.000Z","msg":"好正 無論係間遊戲公司<br />\n定事態發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565fa55f